acknowledgement.excerpt:
In this project I'm try to build low computational human face detection and recognition algorithm on raspberry pi
using opencv and Tensorflow lite for Embedded systems

Application inspired by Facenet architecture using embedding https://arxiv.org/abs/1503.03832
Currently experimenting on
Classifiers
Open cv "haarcascade_frontalface_default" and "haarcascade_eye" classifier

Deep Learning for recognition
MobileNetV2 "Inverted Residuals and Linear Bottlenecks" https://arxiv.org/abs/1801.04381
EfficientNet "Rethinking Model Scaling for Convolutional Neural Networks" https://arxiv.org/abs/1905.11946

Embedding Classifier
SVM
K-mean

Dataset
LFW dataset Labeled Faces in the Wild http://vis-www.cs.umass.edu/lfw
